  • 直系の既知のサブクラス:
    VideoInfoManager

    public class VideoInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by Seo on 2016/12/17. this class stores information of each video note; this class is serializable, but child classes extending this may be not. when passed with Intent, it is safe to convert them to the instance of this class
